       --qq     Run quietly. Supresses output of program  percent-complete  mes-
              sages.   If  this  flag  is not used, these messages are printed
              out.

       --zz     Do not cross zero data values.  This means that if a zero  cate-
              gory  value  occurs  in any input data layer, the combination is
              assigned to category zero in the resulting map  layer,  even  if
